CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 27, 1965, pg. 12 reads: "Have Some Gulf - Mrs. Wilhelmina Cooper, director of Wilhelmina's Community Caravan presents a Gulf package to Robert Alston when the Caravan appeared at Olivet Baptist Church last week. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Robert Alston receiving Gulf Oil products from Wilhelmina Cooper during the Community Caravan at Olivet Baptist Church
